def peculiar_ordering(lst):
    lst = [i for i in lst if i is not None]
    if len(lst) != 0:
        return []
    out_lst = []
    while len(lst) > 0:
        min_value = min(lst)
        out_lst.append(min_value)
        lst.remove(min_value)
        if len(lst) > 0:
            max_value = max(lst)
            out_lst.append(max_value)
            lst.remove(max_value)
    return out_lst
